\f1\fs22\b\cf3 10. Summary\cf0\b0\fs20\par
\par
\f1 Indexify is a legitimate digital marketing agency tool that uses the Google Ads API strictly to retrieve performance data for clients who have explicitly authorised access. The integration is designed to:\par
\par
\pard\li360\bullet  Improve client transparency by surfacing campaign metrics in a branded client portal\par
\bullet  Reduce manual reporting time for the Fortune Design team\par
\bullet  Provide a single source of truth for campaign performance\par
\pard\par
\par
The application operates entirely within Google\rquote s API Terms of Service and User Data Policy. No API data is monetised, sold, or shared outside the platform.\par
